Node.Notes: Perizzites are mentioned more than twenty times in the Old Testament, and are associated with the Canaanites four times. Nothing else is known about them.
Assumes verb "part company" carries over or a verb like "you go."
Mamre apparently refers to a person here, as in Gen 14:13, 24. It refers to a locality in 23:17, 19; 25:9; 49:30; 50:13.
